+{"id":"frankenpandas-rprx9","title":"fd90.230: Cover Series scalar reductions + cumulative ops","description":"fd90.230: Cover Series scalar reductions + cumulative ops.

Series has these reductions/ops at fp-frame:3105-4323 with no integration coverage:
- Reductions returning Scalar: sum, mean, min, max, std, var, median, prod, quantile, abs
- Counts returning usize/Scalar: count, nunique
- Cumulative returning Series: cumsum, cumprod, cummax, cummin

Series.count() has marginal coverage at line 912 ("let count = series.count()").

Scope:
- Extend an existing test (or add new) with all these calls.

